    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019ve got something truly special in my driveway that I know a fellow enthusiast is going to fall in love with. This absolute gem has been my pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and treated to the finest care. It\u2019s in such stunning, pristine condition that it honestly feels like stepping back onto the showroom floor\u2014the paint shines like a mirror and the interior still has that fresh, crisp feel. There might be a tiny, barely-there mark from a stray pebble if you look with a microscope, but for all intents and purposes, she's a total knockout. I\u2019d love for you to swing by, have a chat, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so head-over-heels for this ride!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a masterclass in mechanical synergy and chassis rigidity. This specimen features a meticulously re-mapped ECU optimized for linear power delivery and a reinforced subframe to neutralize lateral torsional loads. The suspension geometry has been surgically dialed in with high-rebound valving and adjusted roll centers for razor-sharp turn-in. The drivetrain is anchored by a precision-balanced flywheel and a short-throw shifter for instantaneous gear synchronization. Every fluid circuit has been flushed with high-temp synthetics, and compression ratios across all cylinders remain within 1% of factory-fresh tolerances. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a high-fidelity instrument of speed, maintained to a standard that puts showroom floor models to shame. Concours-level paint depth meets a cabin that retains its original assembly-line scent.",
      "price": 48950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
