    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the sun dipping below the horizon as you glide through winding coastal roads, the engine\u2019s low growl a symphony of mechanical perfection. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time capsule of elegance. Its deep, obsidian finish catches the moonlight like a still lake, while the hand-stitched leather interior welcomes you with the scent of a private library. Every curve of its silhouette was designed to turn heads and stir the soul. This is your invitation to own a masterpiece that transforms every mundane commute into a grand tour.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
